In the last few years, Linux has become a first-class gaming platform thanks to <ulink url="http://www.valvesoftware.com/">Valve</ulink> bringing the <ulink url="http://store.steampowered.com/"><application>Steam</application></ulink> platform to Linux. At the time of writing, <application>Steam</application> has more than 2000 high-quality indie and AAA titles available for Linux. Ubuntu MATE is fully compatible with <application>Steam</application> for Linux.
