      <para>
While <application>Steam</application> is a major step forward for gaming on Linux, there are also many high quality and enjoyable Open Source games titles available for Ubuntu MATE via the <application>Ubuntu Software Centre</application>. It doesn't matter if you like flight simulators, motor racing, first-person shooters, jump and run or card games, you'll find something to keep you entertained.
      </para>
