The <ulink url="https://ubuntu-mate.boutique/"><guilabel>Shop</guilabel></ulink> link reveals the "Ubuntu MATE Boutique" where you can purchase Entroware computers, pre-installed with Ubuntu MATE, shirts, jackets, mugs, stickers and more!
