Ubuntu MATE is active on <ulink url="https://plus.google.com/communities/108331279007926658904">Google+</ulink>, <ulink url="https://twitter.com/ubuntu_mate">Twitter</ulink>, and <ulink url="https://www.facebook.com/UbuntuMATEedition/">Facebook</ulink>.
